art i makes  economic projections for north korea in the hypothetical event that north korea makes large freemarket reforms right now published on september   the olympics and economics  makes projections for the number of gold medals and told olympic medals that each country wins at the  olympics using economic data and previous olympic data published in  see alsoedit list of former employees of goldman sachs referencesedit notes  a b c d e f g h i j k l m the goldman sachs group inc  form k annual report  quarterly report for the period ended december    goldman sachs locations  like everyone else goldman was in trouble the economist july     how goldman secretly bet on the us housing crash mcclatchy november     goldman sachs to return b of bailout money usa today april     jpmorgan and  other banks repay tarp money the new york times june     spiro leah nathans reed stanley december   inside the money machine–in a bigisall business goldman vows to go it alone bloomberg lp   business  finance cash  comeback timecom november   subscription required  endlich lisa  goldman sachs the culture of success new york aa knopf p  isbn    a b c d e f g h i j k l m n william d cohan  money and power how goldman sachs came to rule the world penguin random house isbn    endlich lisa  goldman sachs the culture of success new york aa knopf p  isbn    cohan william d march   goldman sachss long history of duping its clients washington post   hahn thomas k  timothy q cook and robert k laroche editors ed instruments of the money market pdf seventh ed richmond virginia federal reserve bank of richmond cs maint extra text editors list link  giroux gary december   accounting fraud maneuvering and manipulation past and present business expert press   bess levin october   why i left goldman sachs chapter three my alleged competition dealbreaker   business principles the goldman sachs group inc retrieved january     ramirez anthony november   chairman of goldman will retire the new york t